[IMPORTANT]
If the site supports a function to night/day mode, you need to leave in the default mode to this style works correctly, we recomend you to use some function or program to change between day and night theme in browser/O.S. to improve your experience. You can also enable the option "Force dark mode" above, for invert the colors for all unsupported sites (soon).

*Some sites have styles copied from others greats styles, we're inserting all credits for those creators.

Supported sites list:
- Descomplica [partial];
- Google [partial];
- Musicpleer;
- YouTube ("CleanTube v2" by Sardorbek Usmonov);

